data.description: Prepare to be captivated by this charming pool home, nestled on a generous lot in a highly sought-after location. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by soaring ceilings that create an open and airy atmosphere, with a spacious loft above, adding to the sense of grandeur. Natural light floods the inviting space, illuminating the stunning hardwood floors and showcasing the large windows adorned with elegant plantation shutters. This remarkable home boasts not only its aesthetic appeal but also practicality with two extra bonus rooms, perfect for creating an in-law suite, a home office, or a creative workspace to suit your needs. The heart of the home the kitchen has been beautifully updated with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and undermount lighting underneath the wood cabinetry. Downstairs you’ll find both bedrooms, a bathroom, and a large inside laundry room. Step outside into your own private oasis, where a tranquil screened-in lanai beckons you to unwind beside the lagoon-style pool. Surrounded by brick pavers and lush, mature landscaping featuring beautiful palm trees, the backyard is a haven of serenity and privacy, thanks to the vinyl fence that encloses the space. For those seeking storage or a workshop, a spacious shed awaits your projects and hobbies. Beyond the beauty of the home, you'll appreciate the convenience of covered parking, perfect for your RV or boat, ensuring you have space for all your outdoor adventures. Plus, with no HOA or deed restrictions, you have the freedom to enjoy your property your way. Conveniently located, you'll have quick access to shopping malls, grocery stores, major highways, and airports. Schedule a viewing today, your dream lifestyle awaits!
